wordageddon.model

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • wordageddon.model.User

  • public class User
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a user in the Wordageddon application. This class contains user information including authentication details, personal information, and administrative privileges.
    Since:
    2025
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Gregorio Barberio, Francesco Peluso, Davide Quaranta, Ciro Ronca

        Constructor with ID for creating a User object from database retrieval.
        Parameters:
        id - the unique identifier for the user
        username - the unique username for authentication
        fname - the user's first name
        lname - the user's last name
        password - the user's hashed password
        email - the user's email address
        isAdmin - whether the user has administrative privileges
